# Documentation Update Reminders

## When to Update Documentation

After making any of the following changes, you should update the relevant documentation files:

### Architecture Changes
- Adding new dependencies or changing tech stack → Update [docs/architecture.md](mdc:docs/architecture.md)
- Modifying system design or adding new services → Update [docs/architecture.md](mdc:docs/architecture.md)
- Changing build tools or deployment strategy → Update [docs/architecture.md](mdc:docs/architecture.md)

### API Changes
